The Delivery Route Planner (DRP) app allows to:

* manage delivery routes for documents such as Sales Orders, Purchase Orders, Posted Sales Shipments., Warehouse Receipts., Transfer Orders

* calculate and optimize transfer times / routes through the services made available by the [MAPS]({{<relref "MAPS">}}) app

* calculate weights

* generate shipments from the delivery routes

* export routes in order to use them with other applications, such as Circuit